***   P-like (Pascal-like) Language   ***
1. Constants : numeric, character, float, boolean, string
2. Variables : numeric, character, float, boolean, string
3. Assignment statements : :=
4. Arithmetic operations : +, -, *, /, %, ^, |, &, ~
5. Logical operations : &&, ||, !
6. Conditional operations : ==, !=, <, >, <=, =>
7. Conditional statements : If-else, elseif
8. Iteration loops : for, do-while, while-do
9. Procedures
10. Arrays
11. Advanced Variables - typedef
12. Advanced Procedures - nested procedure, passing procedure to procedure

